  "summaries": [
    {
      "id": 857656,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "HackerOne community member Kaushalendra Dubey (titanrain) has reported a missing sanitisation of user input in the `zone-include.php` script of Revive Adserver 6.0.6 and earlier. A low‑privileged user could exploit the clientid parameter to perform reflected XSS attacks.\n\nInput sanitisation has been improved to ensure that all parameters processed by the script are properly validated.",
